4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring specialists with no prior knowledge. This 16-week program features three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students each. Participants will build a foundation in Windows, Linux, and server administration while gaining practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The bootcamp addresses risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. On completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop